additional_info:
Please note that it's not enough to install this style alone, you will also need to install
https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/custom-javascript-for-web/poakhlngfciodnhlhhgnaaelnpjljija

And add the following code into it (don't forget to check the "jquery 2.1.1" checkbox at the top):
setInterval(function(){
  $('.custom-field-front-badges .badge').each(function() {
    if($('.icon-selection-mode', this).length > 0) {
        $(this).addClass('custom-checkbox');
    }
  });
}, 1000);
